# Pan–Path Generator Dispatcher

Interactive Jupyter notebook for equitable lamp scheduling on an office floor
modelled as C⁺ₙ □ Pₘ.

## Features
* Sliders to pick `n` (lamps per room) and `m` (rooms).
* “Run Animation” – 4-frame equitable colouring demo.
* “Start / Stop Dispatcher” – rotates generators in real time.
* `save_current_preview()` – export the animation to MP4 or GIF.

## Getting Started
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-user>/<repo>.git
cd <repo>
pip install -r requirements.txt   # networkx, matplotlib, ipywidgets
jupyter lab                       # open Pan_Path-Dispatcher.ipynb
